Line is a terrible app. All users, beware! Line does not save your data (chat history). If you transfer your account to a new phone and have not backed up your old phone, all of your chat history will be lost. I am furious that I was not told by LIne prior to transferring my account that my data would not automatically be transferred. I was not told that my old phone's chat history would be deleted. Use Messenger or Viber instead. They are much more convenient AND they keep your data safe.
